## Dismount

---



[Entity Action Type](https://origins.readthedocs.io/en/latest/types/entity_action_types/dismount)

Dismounts the entity from their vehicle.

Type ID: `origins:dismount`




---

### Examples

```json
"entity_action": {
    "type": "origins:dismount"
}
```
